Story 6 — Build Extraction Prompt
As a developer
I want to build the extraction prompt inside the Lambda
So that we send clear and complete instructions to the LLM before calling it
What needs to happen:

Read entity definitions loaded in Story 5
For each entity build a prompt section that includes:

Entity name and description
If CONSTRAINED — include the allowed values list
If OPEN — include the expected format
Example utterance showing how a customer might say it


Embed confidence scoring rules into the prompt:

HIGH if value is clearly stated
MED if value is inferred
LOW if value is ambiguous


Embed validation rules into the prompt:

amount: must be a positive number
date: must be YYYY-MM-DD
routing: must be exactly 9 digits
phone: must be 10 to 11 digits
percentage: must be between 0 and 100


Prompt reviewed by tech lead before moving to next story

Done when:

Prompt is built correctly for both CONSTRAINED and OPEN entities
Confidence and validation rules are embedded
Tech lead has reviewed and approved the prompt output
Unit tests written for prompt structure

