Story 9 — Build Response and Return Status
As a developer
I want to build the final response and determine the correct status
So that the caller receives a clean structured result they can act on
What needs to happen:

Build response as an array of objects
Each entity object contains name, value, description
Accepted entities carry the extracted string value
Rejected entities carry NILL
Append count and missing_count as numbers (not strings)
Serialise the entire array via JSON stringify before returning
Determine status:

missing_count equals 0 → COMPLETE · g_entity_extraction_status true
found_count greater than 0 → PARTIAL · g_entity_extraction_status true
found_count equals 0 → EMPTY · g_entity_extraction_status false



